The '''University of Commenor''' was a [[University/Legends|university]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Commenor/Legends|Commenor]]. In the last days of the [[Separatist Crisis/Legends|Separatist Crisis]], it was the site of a large peace rally; [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala]] made an anti-war speech to the rally, where she included the sentence, ''"Warfare is the product of cowardice; it takes bravery to forego easy answers and find peaceful resolutions."'' The statement&mdash;and by association, Amidala, the University, and the peace movement&mdash;drew widespread criticism from [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] veterans and law-enforcement personnel.

